<li>Don't hesitate to call on me for anything you need.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and offering any practical help you may require.</li>
<li>I'd be happy to run errands, cook meals, or just listen.</li>
<li>Let me know if you need someone to talk to, or just sit with.</li>
<li>I want to help lighten your load during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Please accept my condolences and know I'm here to support you.</li>
<li>My thoughts are with you; reach out if you need anything at all.</li>
